        h3 Dig Deeper
        ul
          li Check out our <a href="/accelerator/digital-health/faq">Frequently Asked Questions.</a>
          li Sign up for our <a href="http://eepurl.com/X9BvP">newsletter!</a>
          li Check out our lovely city, <a href="/locations/spartanburg">Spartanburg.</a>
          li Meet your <a href="/accelerator/mentors">mentors.</a>
          li We offer amazing perks through <a href="http://gan.co">GAN</a> and <a href="http://f6s.com">F6S</a>.
